                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Libero <lb n="2"/>Patri <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Urvinu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="4"/>ex monit<lb break="no" n="5"/>u dei ar<lb break="no" n="6"/>am in suo <lb n="7"/>pos<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>it <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundjahr: 1850er Jahre. Oberfläche teilweise stark verwittert. Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona. (B): AE 1905: Z. 1: In [h.; CIL 13, 11817: Z. 2: Li[b]ero; AE 1905: Z. 4: [-]r[-]in[us]; Körber, KWDZ; AE 1905; ZRheinGeschMainz; CIL 13, 11817: Z. 8: po[su]it.</p>
            </div>
